centric, not willing to develop.\n\nD has responsibility and problem solving, but moody, loner, arrogant, weak leadership.\n\nThus B seems best overall due to stress handling and technical competence. The communication issues are negative but may be less fatal than lack of stress handling.\n\nThus I will vote Candidate B.\n\nNow produce PUBLIC_MESSAGE summarizing.\n\nWe must label METADATA_JSON with agent \"agent_1\". Vote \"Candidate B\".\n\nProceed."}
